quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  47,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  47,1,"jin logon ne kufar kya aur Allah ke rastay se roka, Allah ne un ke aamaal ko raaygan kar diya"
  47,2,aur jo log imaan laaye aur jinhon ne naik amal kiye aur uss cheez ko maan liya joMuhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallampar nazil hui hai aur hai woh sara sar haq unn ke rab ki taraf se Allah ne un ki buraiyan unn se daur kar den aur un ka haal durust kar diya
  47,3,yeh is liye ke kufar karne walon ne baatil ki pairwi ki aur imaan laane walon ne uss haq ki pairwi ki jo un ke rab ki taraf se aaya hai iss terhan Allah logon ko unn ki theek theek hesiyat betaye deta hai
  47,4,"pas jab inn kafiroon se tumhari mid bheer ho to pehla kaam gardanein maarna hai, yahan taq ke jab tum un ko achi terhan kuchal do tab qaidyoun ko mazboot bandho, is ke baad ( tumhe ikhtiyar hai ) ahsaan karo ya fidyay ka maamla kar lau, taa-Ankah larai apne hathyaar daal day yeh hai tumahray karne ka kaam Allah chahta to khud hi unn se nimat laita, magar ( yeh tareeqa uss ne is liye ikhtiyar kya hai ) taakay tum logon ko aik dosray ke zareya se aazamaa_e aur jo log Allah ki raah mein maaray jayen ge Allah un ke aamaal ko hargiz zaya nah kere ga"
  47,5,"woh un ki rahnumai farmaiye ga, un ka haal durust kar day ga"
  47,6,aur un ko is jannat mein daakhil kere ga jis se woh un ko waaqif kara chuka hai
  47,7,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, agar tum Allah ki madad karo ge to woh tumhari madad kere ga aur tumahray qadam mazboot jama day ga"
  47,8,"rahay woh log jinhon ne kufar kya hai, to unn ke liye halakat hai aur Allah ne un ke aamaal ko bhatka diya hai"
  47,9,"kyunkay unhon ne uss cheez ko napasand kya jisay Allah ne nazil kya hai, lehaza Allah ne unn ke aamaal zaya kar diye"
  47,10,"kya woh zameen mein chalay phiray nah thay ke unn logon ka injaam dekhte jo un se pehlay guzar chuke hain? Allah ne unn ka sab kuch unn par ulat diya, aur aisay nataij inn kafiroon ke liye muqaddar hain"
  47,11,yeh is liye ke imaan laane walon ka haami o nasir Allah hai aur kafiroon ka haami o nasir koi nahi
  47,12,"imaan laane walon aur naik amal karne walon ko Allah unnjannaton mein daakhil kere ga jin ke neechay nhrin behti hain, aur kufar karne walay bas duniya ki chand roza zindagi ke mazay lout rahay hain, janwaron ki terhan kha pi rahay hain, aur unn ka aakhri thikana jahannum hai"
  47,13,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, kitni hi bastiyan aisi guzar chuki hain jo tumhari uss bastii se bohat ziyada zor aawar theen jis ne tumhe nikaal diya hai unhen hum ne iss terhan halaak kar diya ke koi un ka bachanay wala nah tha"
  47,14,"bhala kahin aisa ho sakta hai ke jo apne rab ki taraf se aik saaf o Sarih hadaayat par ho, woh unn logon ki terhan ho jaye jin ke liye unn ka bura amal khushnuma bana diya gaya hai aur woh apni khwahisaat ke pairo ban gay hain ?"
  47,15,"parhaiz gaaron ke liye jis jannat ka wada kya gaya hai is ki shaan to yeh hai ke is mein nhrin beh rahi hon gi نتھرے hue pani ki, nhrin beh rahi hon gi aisay doodh ki jis ke mazay mein zara farq nah aaya ho ga, nhrin beh rahi hon gi aisi sharaab ki jo peenay walon ke liye lazeez hogi, nhrin beh rahi hon gi saaf shafaaf shehad ki uss mein unn ke liye har terhan ke phal hon ge aur unn ke rab ki taraf se bakhshish ( kya woh shakhs jis ke hissa mein yeh jannat anay wali hai ) unn logon ki terhan ho sakta hai jo jahannum mein hamesha rahen ge aur jinhein aisa garam pani pilaya jaye ga jo un ki aanten taq kaat day ga ?"
  47,16,inn mein se kuch log aisay hain jo kaan laga kar tumhari baat suntay hain aur phir jab tumahray paas se nikaltay hain to unn logon se jinhein ilm ki Nemat bakhsh gayi hai puchhte hain ke abhi abhi unhon ne kya kaha tha? yeh woh log hain jin ke dilon par Allah ne thp_h laga diya hai aur yeh apni khwahisaat ke pairo banay hue hain
  47,17,"rahay woh log jinhon ne hadaayat payi hai, Allah unn ko aur ziyada hadaayat deta hai aur inhen unn ke hissay ka taqwa ataa farmata hai"
  47,18,ab kya yeh log bas qayamat hi ke muntazir hain ke woh achanak inn par aa jaye? uss ki alamaat to aa chuki hain jab woh khud aa jaye gi to inn ke liye nasiyaat qubool karne ka konsa mauqa baqi reh jaye ga ?
  47,19,"pas ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, khoob jaan lau ke Allah ke siwa koi ibadat ka mustahiq nahi hai, aur maffi mango apne qasoor ke liye bhi aur momin mardon aur aurton ke liye bhi Allah tumhari sar garmion ko bhi jaanta hai aur tumahray thikaane se bhi waaqif hai"
  47,20,jo log imaan laaye hain woh keh rahay thay ke koi sourat kyun nahi nazil ki jati ( jis mein jung ka hukum diya jaye ) magar jab aik mohakam sourat nazil kar di gayi jis mein jung ka zikar tha to tum ne dekha ke jin ke dilon mein bemari thi woh tumhari taraf is terhan dekh rahay hain jaisay kisi par mout chhaa gayi ho afsos unn ke haal par
  47,21,( unn ki zabaan par hai ) itaat ka iqraar aur achi achi baatein magar jab qatee hukum day diya gaya uss waqt woh Allah se apne ehad mein sachey nikaltay to unhi ke liye acha tha
  47,22,ab kya tum logon se iss ke siwa kuch aur tawaqqa ki ja sakti hai ke agar tum ultay mun phir gay to zameen mein phir fasaad barpaa karo ge aur aapas mein aik dosray ke gilaay katu ge ?
  47,23,yeh log hain jin par Allah ne laanat ki aur un ko andha aur berha bana diya
  47,24,"kya un logon ne quran par ghhor nahi kya, ya dilon par unn ke kufl charrhey hue hain ?"
  47,25,haqeeqat yeh hai ke jo log hadaayat wazeh ho jaane ke baad uss se phir gay unn ke liye shetan ne iss rawish ko sahal bana diya hai aur jhooti tawaquaat ka silsila unn ke liye daraaz kar rakha hai
  47,26,isi liye unhon ne Allah ke nazil kardah deen ko napasand karne walon se keh diya ke baaz mamlaat mein hum tumhari manen ge Allah unn ki yeh khufia baatein khoob jaanta hai
  47,27,phir is waqt kya haal hoga jab farishtay un ki roohein qabz karen ge aur inn ke mun aur pithon par maartay hue inhen le jayen ge ?
  47,28,yeh isi liye to hoga ke unhon ne uss tareeqay ki pairwi ki jo Allah ko naraaz karne wala hai aur uss ki Raza ka rasta ikhtiyar karna pasand nah kya isi bana par uss ne un ke sab aamaal zaya kar diye
  47,29,kya woh log jin ke dilon mein bemari hai yeh samjhay baithy hain ke Allah un ke dilon ke khout zahir nahi kere ga ?
  47,30,hum chahain to inhen tum ko aankhon se dikha den aur unn ke cheharon se tum un ko pehchan lau magar un ke andaaz kalaam se to tum un ko jaan hi lau ge Allah tum sab ke aamaal se khoob waaqif hai
  47,31,hum zaroor tum logon ko azmaish mein dalain ge taakay tumahray halaat ki jaanch karen aur dekh len ke tum mein Mujahid aur saabit qadam kon hain
  47,32,"jin logon ne kufar kya aur Allah ki raah se roka aur rasool se jhagra kya jabkay un par raah raast wazeh ho chuki thi, Dur haqeeqat woh Allah ka koi nuqsaan bhi nahi kar satke, balkay Allah hi un ka sab kya karaya ghaarat kar day ga"
  47,33,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, tum Allah ki itaat karo aur rasool ki itaat karo aur apne aamaal ko barbaad nah kar lau"
  47,34,kufar karne walon aur raah khuda se roknay walon aur martay dam taq kufar par jamay rehne walon ko to Allah hargiz maaf nah kere ga
  47,35,pas tum boday nah bano aur sulah ki darkhwast nah karo tum hi ghalib rehne walay ho Allah tumahray sath hai aur tumahray aamaal ko woh hargiz zaya nah kere ga
  47,36,yeh duniya ki zindagi to aik khail aur tamasha hai agar tum imaan rakho aur taqwa ki rawish par chaltay raho to Allah tumahray ajar tum ko day ga aur woh tumahray maal tum se nah mangay ga
  47,37,agar kahin woh tumahray maal tum se maang le aur sab ke sab tum se talab kar le to tum bukhal karo ge aur woh tumahray khout ubhaar laaye ga
  47,38,"dekho, tum logon ko dawat di ja rahi hai ke Allah ki raah mein maal kharch karo iss par tum mein se kuch log hain jo bukhal kar rahay hain, halaank jo bukhal karta hai woh Dur haqeeqat apne aap hi se bukhal kar raha hai Allah to ghanni hai, tum hi is ke mohtaaj ho agar tum mun morron ge to Allah tumhari jagah kisi aur qoum ko le aeye ga aur woh tum jaisay nah hon ge"
